## Success criteria

PSCL is working if:

- concepts are retrievable by meaning, not only wording
- doctrine compresses cleanly into stable semantic records
- cross-domain mappings are explicit and auditable
- operators can recover old insights without rereading entire threads
- Pantheon gains a legible latent structure rather than a heap of beautiful fragments

